"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/576998","Ministry of Defence","false","2016-09-14","<p>Refits of RFA DILIGENCE were carried out from June 2012 to February 2013, and from September 2014 to February 2015, costing £17.6 million and £11 million respectively.</p><p> </p><p>The timings of the refits were driven by factors including the mandatory requirements to renew safety and environmental certification and the need to address equipment obsolescence issues.</p>",,"Earl Howe","HL1596","2016-09-14T16:36:57.01Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/576998/answer","Biography information for Earl Howe","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/576998/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/576998/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2016-09-06","RFA Diligence","2","House of Lords","To ask Her Majesty’s Government what was the cost of the refit to RFA Diligence in 2013 to extend its life to 2020.","false","Biography information for Lord West of Spithead",,"Lord West of Spithead","HL1595"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/576999","Ministry of Defence","false","2016-09-14","<p>Refits of RFA DILIGENCE were carried out from June 2012 to February 2013, and from September 2014 to February 2015, costing £17.6 million and £11 million respectively.</p><p> </p><p>The timings of the refits were driven by factors including the mandatory requirements to renew safety and environmental certification and the need to address equipment obsolescence issues.</p>",,"Earl Howe","HL1595","2016-09-14T16:36:56.933Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/576999/answer","Biography information for Earl Howe","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/576999/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/576999/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2016-09-06","RFA Diligence","2","House of Lords","To ask Her Majesty’s Government what was the cost of the refit to RFA Diligence in 2015.","false","Biography information for Lord West of Spithead",,"Lord West of Spithead","HL1596"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/577000","Ministry of Defence","false","2016-09-14","<p>Since the refit that completed in February 2015, RFA DILIGENCE has not been fully manned by Royal Fleet Auxiliary personnel. In addition, personnel supplied by contractors ensure that the safety and integrity of the ship is maintained until she goes out of service in December 2016.</p>",,"Earl Howe",,"2016-09-14T15:26:04.583Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/577000/answer","Biography information for Earl Howe","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/577000/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/577000/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2016-09-06","RFA Diligence","2","House of Lords","To ask Her Majesty’s Government whether RFA Diligence has been fully manned since her refit in 2015.","false","Biography information for Lord West of Spithead",,"Lord West of Spithead","HL1597"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/577001","Department for Education","false","2016-09-19","<p>Final data for 2014/15 show that there were no Level 5 or Level 6 Construction Industry Training Board (CITB) NVQ diploma achievements in the construction, planning and the built environment sector subject area.</p><p> </p><p>Data reported so far for August to April of the 2015/16 academic year also show that there were no Level 5 or Level 6 CITB NVQ diploma achievements in the construction sector subject area. The data for 2015/16 are subject to change as further data returns relating to the period are received later in the year.</p>",,"Lord Nash",,"2016-09-19T12:41:17.537Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/577001/answer","Biography information for Lord Nash","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/577001/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/577001/answer",,,,,"60","Education","Education","2016-09-06","Construction: National Vocational Qualifications","2","House of Lords","To ask Her Majesty’s Government how many level 5 and level 6 Construction Industry Training Board Construction NVQ diplomas were awarded in (1) 2014, and (2) 2015.","false","Biography information for Baroness Wolf of Dulwich",,"Baroness Wolf of Dulwich","HL1598"
